                <h4 class="text-body mb-4">
                    Every champion has at some point been a competitor who refused to be beaten.
                      <em>Sylvester Stallone</em>
                </h4>
                <p class="mb-4">For those who set out to start an exercise routine and choose to join a gym, the first step is often the most difficult, but also the most important. Entering the world of fitness can be an experience full of excitement and anticipation, but also uncertainty and questions. Once they've made the decision to take the plunge, many are faced with questions about how to get started, what equipment to use, and how to set realistic goals.</p>
                <div class="rounded bg-dark p-5">
