                        <li class="nav-item w-50">
                            <a class="nav-link text-uppercase text-center w-100 active" data-bs-toggle="pill" href="#pills-1">About Us</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item w-50">
                            <a class="nav-link text-uppercase text-center w-100" data-bs-toggle="pill" href="#pills-2">Why Choose Us</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="tab-content">
                        <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="pills-1">
                            <p class="text-secondary mb-0">
                                In our gym, we offer a variety of state-of-the-art equipment suitable for any type of workout, from cardio to strength and flexibility training. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned athlete, you have access to all the resources you need to reach your full potential.
                                With qualified and experienced trainers, we are here to guide and motivate you every step of your fitness journey. From one-on-one personalized training sessions to lively and inspiring group classes, we offer the support and guidance you need to achieve your goals.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="pills-2">
                            <p class="text-secondary mb-0">
                                With us, you'll not only find state-of-the-art equipment and varied training programs, but also a dedicated community that supports and encourages you every step of the way on your fitness journey. Our passionate and well-trained instructors are here to guide and motivate you to push your limits and achieve your goals.
                                But it's not just about physical training - at our gym, we promote a balanced lifestyle that combines exercise, nutrition and mental well-being. In addition to intense workouts, we also offer relaxation and recovery programs such as yoga and massage to help keep your body and mind in tip-top shape.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
